Description:
You arrive at the Happy Owl inn and notice that the tavern has a very peculiar tricolor flag on the door.

Inside the tavern the atmosphere is cold despite the lit fireplace and the faces of the few elves sheltering from the cold do not look very happy.

The innkeeper approaches you and asks you what brings you here and if you need anything.
DescriptionAction: This might be a good time to rest or to get some information.
